data.description:
A perfect small starter home in a friendly neighborhood. Located in the middle of a church, a park, an elementary school and middle school. Carries two bedrooms and one bathroom. Each bedroom closet has built in storage shelves and drawers. Floor plan is spacious and open. No awkward doorways. Plantation shutters on the front windows. Galley style kitchen with brand new cabinet bases installed in January 2021. Kitchen has built in glass top stove and a stack cabinet with oven and microwave built in. Laundry/Utility room located off the kitchen with carport access. 

Home upgrades:

New overhead PVC piping for kitchen and bathroom in December 2020
Cabinet bases installed in kitchen January 2021
Vinyl laminate flooring throughout in 2020
Sewer line replaced in 2016
Hot water heater replaced in 2013
Brand new roof in August 2020
Hurricane windows and shutters replaced in 2005
A/C, electrical work and drywall replaced in 2004

Vinyl laminate flooring in all throughout the house except in the laundry room and bathroom, which has standard tile flooring. Small, cozy screened in lanai with a spacious, open back yard.
